The paper discusses the challenges and opportunities of integrating and processing multimodal data using advanced technologies such as sensors, networked systems, and high-speed data communication and computing. This topic is highly relevant to several subfields of computer science, including artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), social and information networks (cs.SI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
